snippet.title: Shadow Labyrinth – Release Date Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Shadow Labyrinth is coming to Nintendo Switch on July 18, 2025!
 
Phase shift between Swordsman No. 8, Mini PUCK, and GAIA to discover secrets and consume your foes in this genre-twisting take on PAC-MAN. On this mysterious world, it’s eat or be eaten, to survive you must consume darkness.
 
#ShadowLabyrinth #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/
